flowchart TD
    A[Start create_cloze<br/>for each note id] --> B{Target / lemma / hint<br/>fields exist?}
    B -- No --> B1[Increment skipped_missing_field] --> Z
    B -- Yes --> C{Cloze already exists?}
    C -- Yes --> C1[Tag CLOZE_EXISTING<br/>increment skipped_no_change] --> Z
    C -- No --> D[Read Lemma,<br/>Word Definition]
    D --> E{Lemma list empty?}
    E -- Yes --> E1[Increment skipped_missing_field] --> Z
    E -- No --> F[Split Lemma by commas]
    F --> G{Comma found / multiple lemmas?}
    G -- Yes --> H[Parse Word Definition lines<br/>as lemma: definition]
    H --> I[Split note into one note per lemma<br/>and keep only matching definition]
    I --> J[Increment created_notes<br/>and deferred_multi_lemma]
    J --> Z

    G -- No --> K[Use single lemma hint]
    K --> L[Run _apply_cloze_to_note]
    L --> M{Updated?}
    M -- No --> N[Maybe tag CLOZE_FAILED<br/>or CLOZE_INCORRECT_PARSE] --> Z
    M -- Yes --> O[Write cloze, maybe tag CLOZE_NO_STRONG,<br/>update counters and save note when not dry_run] --> Z
